Okular is a universal document viewer. It's multi-platform, fast and 
packed with features, allowing the user to read PDF documents, comics and 
EPub books, browse images, visualize Markdown documents, and much more.

The viewer supports many formats, including PDF, EPub, DjVU and MD for 
documents; JPEG, PNG, GIF, Tiff, WebP for images; CBR and CBZ for comics; 
and many more.

Okular comes with advanced PDF editing features like annotation and 
signing support.
